title: THE BEATLES - Watching The Wheels FLAC
description:
THE BEATLES - Watching The Wheels
Imagine if The Beatles had not disbanded and, after having released a double LP in 1971 (That Would Be Something), and a double LP in 1975 (Don't Make Me Wait Too Long), they then released a double LP in 1981...Watching The Wheels.  Using 1976-1981 solo material this attempts to create a 1981 Beatles album that fits on a single CD or double vinyl LP.
